Functional test #1

UTest platform training Test Case

MacOS Monterey 12.7.6 - Search Results Page - Sorting by Descending price gives incorrect results

Action Performed
1. Visit https://www.*protectingwebsite*.es/

2. Optional: Log in
3. In the search field, type: iphone
4. Sort by: precios caros a barato
5. Scroll down until you find the first example: *protecting item name* para Iphone.

Expected Result
The page should sort the items by final price and show the more expensive ones before the cheaper ones

Actual Result
The page is sorting the items in the wrong order as is considering the original price to place them, rather than the discounted one.
